      "title": "Train continues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Deputy General Superintendent of Railways Mr. Gamini Senaviratne said that due to the imposition of curfew in the Western Province, the trains have not been suspended so far.",
        "The Deputy General Superintendent of Railways said that the decision about the train should be taken by the General Manager of Railways Dhammika Jayasundara."
      ],
